In this modification, after loading the data from Hive, we check if the `prayerData` is empty. If it is, we initialize it with default values based on the constants defined in the `constants.dart` file. We iterate over the years and months specified by `kDefaultStartYear` and `kDefaultEndYear`, and create a `PrayerData` instance for each year and month with default values.

After initializing the `prayerData`, we save it to Hive using the `savePrayerData` method.

With these changes, the app will load default prayer data based on the constants when it runs for the first time, and the home page will update automatically when the prayers are updated.

